{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapSnapshotter(im)addAnnotation:","title":"addAnnotation:"},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"annotation","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation object to add to the receiver. This object","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"must conform to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol. The snapshotter retains the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation object.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects cannot be added to the snapshotter at this time."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any multipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, shape or point collection"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that is specified is silently ignored."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Note"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter."}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" generates static raster images of the map. Each snapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"asynchronously, calling "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" methods if defined, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the snapshot are finished loading."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotter","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","abstract":[{"text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshot":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An image generated by a snapshotter object."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","title":"MLNMapSnapshot","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshot"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshot","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"disconnected vertices, specified as ","type":"text"},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instances. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"orchard."}],"title":"MLNPointCollection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","title":"MLNPolyline","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotOptions":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The options to use when creating images with the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotoptions","title":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","title":"MLNMultiPolyline","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotation:":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"addAnnotation:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter."}]}}}